Message: They proposed to do what I'm proposing you. Helping me with the cameras to keep the government from having images of my face.
I will make them believe I'm counting on them. But you'll be the one covering me from the shadows.

Possible Answers: Are you sure I don't risk anything?
Reactions: I did what was needed to keep you anonymous, don't worry.

Message: I will disconnect for a few hours, and I'll send you a message before going in the building so I can brief you, ok?
